@startuml sequence_paginate
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sort + Infinite scroll

actor User
participant "SearchResultsPage" as UI
participant "SearchApi" as SVC
participant "POST /api/search" as API

User -> UI: tap Sort, pick "Most recent"
UI -> UI: sort.set('recency'); reset page=1
UI -> SVC: search({q, sort:recency, page:1})
SVC -> API: POST
API --> SVC: 200 { nextPage:2, results:[50] }
SVC --> UI: results.set(...)
UI --> User: rows reordered newest-first

User -> UI: scroll near bottom
UI -> UI: loadMore()
UI -> SVC: search({page:2})
SVC -> API: POST
API --> SVC: 200 { nextPage:3, results:[50] }
SVC --> UI: results.append(...)
UI --> User: more rows appear

@enduml
